
ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_Locale: ( ti_Tag = $80080032 )

Specify in ti_Data the Locale that
ASL should use for the text.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_PositiveText: ( ti_Tag = $80080012 )

Specify a pointer to a null terminated
string in ti_Data, to provide the text for
the "OK" gadget.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_NegativeText: ( ti_Tag = $80080013 )

Specify a pointer to a null terminated
string in ti_Data, to provide the text for
the "Cancel" gadget.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_Flags1: ( ti_Tag = $80080014 )

"OR" together the following flags in ti_Data:

FRF_FILTERFUNC    ( = $80 )
FRF_INTUIFUNC     ( = $40 )
FRF_DOSAVEMODE    ( = $20 )
FRF_PRIVATEIDCMP  ( = $10 )
FRF_DOMULTISELECT ( = $ 8 )
FRF_DOPATTERNS    ( = $ 1 )

See the Tag equivalents for descriptions.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_Flags2: ( ti_Tag = $80080016 )

"OR" together the following flags in ti_Data:

FRF_DRAWERSONLY   ( = $1 )
FRF_FILTERDRAWERS ( = $2 )
FRF_REJECTICONS   ( = $4 )

See the Tag equivalents for descriptions.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_DoSaveMode: ( ti_Tag = $8008002C )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to get
an ASL Save requester.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_DoMultiSelect: ( ti_Tag = $8008002D )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to get
a MultiSelect capable requester.

Entries chosen will be specified by:

fr_NumArgs = number of entries chosen.
fr_ArgList = pointer to array of WBArg structs.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_DoPatterns: ( ti_Tag = $8008002E )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to get
a requester with a Patterns gadget.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_DrawersOnly: ( ti_Tag = $8008002F )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to get
a requester with no file entries.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_FilterFunc: ( ti_Tag = $80080031 )

Specify a pointer to a custom Hook function 
to be used for filtering files.
(See the RKM's for more details).


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_RejectIcons: ( ti_Tag = $8008003C )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to
prohibit the display of .info files 
in the requester.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_RejectPattern: ( ti_Tag = $8008003D )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to
prohibit the display of files matching
the pattern in the requester.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_AcceptPattern: ( ti_Tag = $8008003E )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to
only display files matching the pattern 
in the requester.


ASL FileRequester Tags
======================

Usage: AllocAslRequest_/AslRequest_

ASLFR_FilterDrawers: ( ti_Tag = $8008003F )

Specify a True boolean in ti_Data to
also apply the pattern filter to drawers
in the requester.


